Package: collegehoops
Type: Package
Title: Functions to Scrape NCAA Basketball Data
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Derek J. Hanson
Maintainer: <dhanson@utexas.edu>
Description: A series of functions for gathering college basketball data from the web.
    Useful for gathering play-by-play, odds-data, box-scores, and other useful game-level information.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
